Careers
For Careers/Application questions or concerns, please contact HII Talent Acquisition.






Employee Information Line
During weather incidents, emergencies and other situations affecting company operations, employees are advised to call the Employee Information Phone Line for instructions and information.
HII corporate employees working in or near Newport News should follow updates for Newport News Shipbuilding; corporate employees working in or near Pascagoula or other Gulf Coast sites should follow updates for Ingalls Shipbuilding. Employees who are working at sites different from those stated above (i.e., Washington, D.C. office) should follow directions provided to them by their site or facility manager.
To access the Employee Information Phone Line, call (877) 871-2058, then:

Press 1 for Newport News Shipbuilding
Press 2 for Ingalls Shipbuilding
Press 3 for AMSEC
