  Home  Stocks  dividend announcements  Huntington Ingalls Industries, Inc. (NYSE:HII) announces a quarterly dividend of $0.60     Stocksdividend announcements  Huntington Ingalls Industries, Inc. (NYSE:HII) announces a quarterly dividend of $0.60  ByME Staff -July 26, 2017 0  Share on Facebook
Tweet on Twitter


 Huntington Ingalls Industries, Inc. (NYSE:HII) to go ex-dividend.On 7/26/2017 Huntington Ingalls Industries, Inc. ( NYSE:HII ) announced that it will be issuing a quarterly dividend in the amount of $0.60 down from $0.60 making the yield 1.18%.Huntington Ingalls Industries, Inc. (NYSE:HII) Ex- dividend dateHuntington Ingalls Industries, Inc. (NYSE:HII) is set to go ex-dividend on 8/23/2017 and will be payable on 9/8/2017 Dividend History for Huntington Ingalls Industries, Inc. (NYSE:HII) The next payable dividend for Huntington Ingalls Industries, Inc. is scheduled for 9/8/2017. There is an annual dividend of $$2.40 with a yield of 1.18% The company’s dividend has increased by 61.30% on a 3 Year Average The payout ration for the trailing 12 months of earnings is 20.29% , 21.54% based on this years estimates and 20.32% based on next years projected estimates.Recent Dividend History for Huntington Ingalls Industries, Inc. (NYSE:HII) 

On 2/4/2013 Huntington Ingalls Industries, Inc. announced a quarterly dividend of $0.10.
On 5/2/2013 Huntington Ingalls Industries, Inc. announced a quarterly dividend of $0.10.
On 8/9/2013 Huntington Ingalls Industries, Inc. announced a quarterly dividend of $0.10.
On 10/31/2013 Huntington Ingalls Industries, Inc. announced a quarterly dividend of $0.20.
On 2/25/2014 Huntington Ingalls Industries, Inc. announced a quarterly dividend of $0.20.
On 5/1/2014 Huntington Ingalls Industries, Inc. announced a quarterly dividend of $0.20.

