Our Products







San Antonio-class LPDsLPD 17 provides the Navy and Marine Corps with modern, sea based platforms for execution of Expeditionary Warfare Missions.









America-class LHAsLarge deck amphibious assault ships are the flagships of amphibious ready groups and are designed to provide Command and Control.









Arleigh Burke-class DDGsArleigh Burke-class Destroyers, equipped with the Navy's Aegis Combat System, are the most advanced state-of-the-art surface combatants built in the world. 









Legend-class National Security CuttersThe National Security Cutter is the flagship of the Coast Guard fleet, the most technically advanced high endurance cutter in existence.












